# Title: Uncommon Process Access Rights For Target Image
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems), frack113
# Date: 2024-05-27
# Level: low
# Description: Detects process access request to uncommon target images with a "PROCESS_ALL_ACCESS" access mask.
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.stealth, attack.t1055.011
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_access/proc_access_win_susp_all_access_uncommon_target.yml

GrantedAccess="0x1FFFFF" TargetImage IN ("*\\calc.exe", "*\\calculator.exe", "*\\mspaint.exe", "*\\notepad.exe", "*\\ping.exe", "*\\wordpad.exe", "*\\write.exe")